one_reviews_text:
I liked this game. 
It was fun to weave through traffic and dodge the goofy cars. I liked the train level where you had to cross the tracks at the right timing. The sound effects were funny. Getting hit by vehicles was intense in VR but also funny to see my guy ragdoll through the air. 
Great for the price.

review_title: You are not authorized to play this game
one_reviews_text:
The game will not allow me to play. It gives me an error: "You are not authorized to play this game."

Worthless
review_feedback: We apologize for the inconvenience. That message should only appear if you have not purchased the game through the store or Oculus was unable to verify your purchase for some reason. Make sure you have an internet connection when you launch it.
